00:09:03.792 --> 00:09:05.250
ANI DIFRANCO: Yeah
no, that's cool.

00:09:05.250 --> 00:09:06.730
I love coming back to New York.

00:09:06.730 --> 00:09:07.230
I do.

00:09:07.230 --> 00:09:08.970
I do.

00:09:08.970 --> 00:09:12.910
I used to miss it like
