00:40:53.020 --> 00:40:55.600
Me, it's about me now.

00:40:55.600 --> 00:40:57.955
And so that was
hard as an artist.

00:41:00.690 --> 00:41:02.610
The little guy, I have
a four-year-old son,

00:41:02.610 --> 00:41:05.120
and he's the same way.

00:41:05.120 --> 00:41:09.540
But as soon as Petah decided,
I want to be a part of that,

00:41:09.540 --> 00:41:11.430
then it became our thing.

00:41:11.430 --> 00:41:13.560
It was not my thing anymore.

00:41:13.560 --> 00:41:17.430
And it changed the
whole atmosphere

00:41:17.430 --> 00:41:21.210
around music, which is
just thrilling to me.

00:41:21.210 --> 00:41:23.910
I love to sing, but I love
to sing with my daughter

00:41:23.910 --> 00:41:25.500
even more.

00:41:25.500 --> 00:41:29.580
So yeah, now that we can make
it something we do together,

00:41:29.580 --> 00:41:33.810
it's opened up a
whole new era for us.

00:41:33.810 --> 00:41:35.810
MATTHEW HENDERSHOT: Thank
